== Veliki čelnik ==
At the beginning of the 15th century, during the [[Serbian Despotate]], the title of ''veliki čelnik'' was the equivalent of [[count palatine]] and was the highest court title, with the title-holders holding great provinces, property and honours. Of these, [[Radič, Grand Čelnik|Radič]] ({{floruit}} 1413–41) was the most notable.

== List of incumbent veliki čelniks ==
* [[Jovan Oliver]], veliki čelnik, served Stefan Dušan (before 1340){{sfn|Blagojević|2001|p=212}}
* [[Dimitrije (veliki čelnik)|Dimitrije]], veliki čelnik, served Stefan Dušan (before 1349), {{sfn|Blagojević|2001|p=212}} then Uroš V (fl. 1359)
* [[Hrebeljan]], veliki čelnik, served Stefan Lazarević (fl. 1405){{sfn|Srejović|Gavrilović|Ćirković|1982|p=120}}
* [[Radoslav (veliki čelnik)|Radoslav]], 
* [[Radič (veliki čelnik)|Radič]], veliki? čelnik, served Stefan Lazarević.
* [[Radič (veliki čelnik)|Radič]], served Đurađ Branković (fl. 1429)
* [[Mihailo Anđelović]] (fl. 1458), served Đurađ and Lazar Branković.

